{"uuid":"recommended281200","createDate":1626232560000,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"281200\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:08:36\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2021-07-14\",\"gameName\":\"A Boy and His Blob\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/281200\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/281200/\",\"playTime\":\"12.5\",\"updateTime\":\"2021-07-14\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"12.5\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/281200\"}","title":"评测 > A Boy and His Blob","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n 非常棒的解谜游戏，小男孩遇到了小小变形怪，还成为了好朋友~\n <br>\n 然后开始冒险探索收集各种奇怪宝箱装饰自己的小房间！\n <br>\n <br>\n 故事情节好像很简单，变形怪从变形星球坐火箭到主角的星球！\n <br>\n 然后坠落，小男孩出于好奇去查看。互相就这么成了好友了！\n <br>\n 哦不，可能是宠物也说不定···\n <br>\n <br>\n 小男孩可以爱抚变形怪，还能丢种子让变形怪变成各种各样有利于过关的小物件！\n <br>\n 比如：弹床、气球、楼梯、千斤顶、降落伞、铁球、弹球、大气泡···等等等等\n <br>\n 后期好像还能变成机甲！甚至是和主角一样的人！？\n <br>\n 咦！人！？<span class=\"bb_spoiler\"><span> 我突然有种更新奇的玩法···emmm~ </span></span>\n <br>\n 好吧，其实我没玩到那部分···\n <br>\n <br>\n 解谜部分前期简单，后期越来越难，似乎有好多地图，从原始深林到城市···后面的没解锁~QAQ~\n <br>\n 我只过到第二张地图的最后一关卡了~QAQ~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2546596533\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2546596533</a>\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2547511636\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2547511636</a>\n <br>\n <br>\n ~感觉游戏里最好玩的还是那个可以像骑马一样骑在上面的弹球最好玩~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2545737072\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_2\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2545737072</a>\n <br>\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  ~好游戏不需要中文~指引都没啥文字~\n  <br>\n  ~有好多个Boss~我就打过了第一个Boss···\n  <br>\n  ~后面的Boss不是打不过~\n  <br>\n  ~而是我压根没资格见到~QAQ~\n  <br>\n  ~哎~说的好像遇到了我就能打过似的~噗~\n </